      "content": "that makes sense. so if the bacteria are helping to inhibit \"undesirable\" stuff, what exactly determines the balance between the yeast and the LAB? i'm wondering if there's some kind of hidden microbial competition going on that i can't see, causing that inconsistency in the rise.",
